<lb n="7" break="no"/>rājula besta yellebōyini ko 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḍuku nāgana bōyiṁḍu 
<lb n="9"/>rāmēśvaradēvarakuṁnu vīragaṇa 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>mulu(la)kuṁnu majjanamu sē 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>yanu Udakālaku nuyyi 
<lb n="12"/>dravviṁci kaṭṭapade gaṭṭiṁce 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>nu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> maṁgaḷamahā śrī 
